data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!! Come fall in love with this warm and inviting 2017-built home in the highly sought-after Arlington Ridge 55+ community in Central Florida! This gorgeous, quiet cul-de-sac, 3-bedroom home offers a large study/den that can easily be used as a 4th bedroom or private office. This meticulously-maintained home comes with a large eat-in kitchen including a gas stove, ample granite countertops, and tons of natural light. Every room in the home has beautiful views, and the large screened patio overlooks the golf course and pond with breathtaking sunsets. This solar-powered, natural gas home comes with easy-close plantation shutters and a security system. The indoor laundry room and tandem golf cart garage add to the home's comforts. There are wonderful storage cabinets in the garage that will stay with the home. Home furnishings may be negotiated separately. The community offers awesome amenities including a clubhouse, restaurant, golf course, 24-hour guarded gate, resort-style pool, lap pool, fitness center, tennis courts, and so many activities. Located just a few minutes from fabulous Lake Harris, great for boating and other water activities. Easy commute to anywhere you want to visit in Central Florida and beyond via the Florida Turnpike. Schedule your showing to see this unique gem before it's gone!
